<head>	
	
	<title>
		
		<%= ((@postStatus == 'new') ? "NewPost" : ((@postStatus == 'edit') ? "EditPost" : "BlogPost")) %> :: RBlog
		 
	</title>
	
	<link href="/assets/templatemo_style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
	
	<script type="text/javascript" >
		
		document.getElementById("templatemo_rss").style="display:none;";
		
	</script>
	
	<style type="text/css">
		
		input, textarea  {
			
			width: 100%;
			padding: 10px;
			margin: 10px;
			
		}
		
		textarea {
			
			height: 40%;
			
		}
		
		#submit_post {
			
			width: auto;
			float: right;
			
		}
		
		#cancel_post {
			
			width: auto;
			float: left;
			
		}
		
		form {
			
			margin-top: 10px;
			margin-bottom: 80px;
			
		}
		
	</style>
	
</head>

<body>
    
    <div id="templatemo_right_column">
        
        <div id="templatemo_main">
        
        <% if(@postStatus == 'new' || @postStatus == 'edit')  %>
        
        	<div class="post_section" class="new edit" >
        		
        		<h2>New Post</h2>
        		
        		<%= form_for(:blog_post, :url => ((@postStatus == 'new') ? {:action => 'new'} : {:action => 'edit', :postId => @rblog.id})) do |form| %>
        			
        			<%= form.text_field(:author, :placeholder => "Author", :required => true, :value => ((@rblog == nil) ? "" : @rblog.author)) %>
        			<%= form.text_field(:post_title, :placeholder => "Blog Post Title", :required => true, :value => ((@rblog == nil) ? "" : @rblog.post_title)) %>
        			<%= form.text_area(:post_message, :placeholder => "Blog Post Message", :required => true, :value => ((@rblog == nil) ? "" : @rblog.post_message)) %>
        			<%= form.submit(:id => "submit_post", :value => ((@postStatus == 'new') ? 'Post' : 'Update')) %>
        			
        		<% end %>
        		
        	</div>
        	
        <% else %>
        
        	
            <div class="post_section" class="old" >
            	
                <h2> <%= @rblog.post_title %> </h2>
    
                <%= link_to("Edit", :action => 'blog_post', :postStatus => 'edit', :postId => "#{@postId}") %> <strong> | </strong>
        		<%= link_to("Delete", :action => 'delete', :postId => "#{@postId}") %> <strong> | </strong>
        		<strong>Author:</strong> <%= @rblog.author %> <strong> | </strong> <%= @rblog.updated_at.to_datetime.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %> <br />
                
              	<p> <%= simple_format(@rblog.post_message) %> </p>
              	
		  	</div>
            
            <div class="comment_tab">Comments</div>
            
      		<div id="comment_section">
                
                <ol class="comments first_level">
                        
                        <li>
                            <div class="comment_box commentbox1">
                                    
                                <div class="gravatar">
                                    <img src="images/avator.png" alt="author" />
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="comment_text">
                                    <div class="comment_author">Steve<span class="date">December 10, 2048</span><span class="time">12:30 AM</span></div>
                                    <p>Phasellus mattis tellus eu risusLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
                                  <div class="reply"><a href="#">Reply</a></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cleaner"></div>
                            </div>                        
                            
                        </li>
                        
                        <li>
                        
                        
                            	<ol class="comments">
                            
                                    <li>
                                        <div class="comment_box commentbox2">
                                        
                                        <div class="gravatar">
                                        <img src="images/avator.png" alt="author 2" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="comment_text">
                                        <div class="comment_author">Ethan<span class="date">December 14, 2048</span><span class="time">10:20 AM</span></div>
                                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. </p>
                                        <div class="reply"><a href="#">Reply</a></div>
                                        </div>
                                        
                                        <div class="cleaner"></div>
                                        </div>                        
                                    
                                    
                                    </li>
                                    
                                    <li>
                                    
                            
                                        <ol class="comments">
                                    
                                            <li>
                                                <div class="comment_box commentbox1">
                                                
                                                    <div class="gravatar">
                                                        <img src="images/avator.png" alt="author 3" />
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="comment_text">
                                                        <div class="comment_author">Walker<span class="date">December 18, 2048</span><span class="time">11:45 PM</span></div>
                                                        <p>Donec nunc neque, pulvinar a, vestibulum eget, luctus id, orci.   Pellentesque elementum enim a augue. Donec in nisi. <a href="#">Etiam sit amet turpis</a>.</p>
                                                      <div class="reply"><a href="#">Reply</a></div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    
                                                    <div class="cleaner"></div>
                                                </div>                        
                                                
                                                
                                            </li>
                                    
                                        </ol>
                        
                        			</li>
                                </ol>
                                
						</li>
                        
                        <li>
                            <div class="comment_box commentbox2">
                                    
                                     
                                <div class="gravatar">
                                    <img src="images/avator.png" alt="author 4" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="comment_text">
                                    <div class="comment_author">Steve<span class="date">December 24, 2048</span><span class="time">10:55 AM</span></div>
                                    <p>Nam sodales, pede vel dapibus lobortis, ipsum diam molestie risus, a vulputate risus nisl pulvinar lacus.</p>
